The motion quartet. We presented the motion quartet stimulus inducing a similar illusory horizontal and vertical motion as the presented physical horizontal and vertical motion stimuli (Fig. 1A): the physical and the ambiguous motion quartet were designed as described in Schneider et al. (2019). The quartet is composed of four squares \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
